data.description: PEACEFUL SETTING :  Here we have a charming 3 bedroom ranch home situated in a peaceful country setting surrounded by nature. This home features a bright and airy eat-in kitchen with ample cupboard space complete with appliances making it a delightful space to entertain and enjoy a meal. The living room of this home features a cozy corner fireplace adding warmth and ambiance for the chilly evenings ahead. Additionally, there is a convenient first floor laundry area directly off of the kitchen to make doing laundry a breeze! The master bedroom boasts a private master bath providing a comfortable retreat. Outside you'll find a large covered porch perfect for relaxing and enjoying the scenic surroundings. To accommodate your vehicles and storage needs, there's a detached 3 car garage just waiting for you. Take action now and call to schedule your private showing to make this home yours and start creating memories in your new home.
